{"tid":1851533,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"既然廢老買口罩買到你咁燥 不如拍賣 價高者得啦","createTime":"2020-01-30T05:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T05:47:04.000Z","uid":275197,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"92376a7802a31e472d825616b21ba138db2010eb","tid":1851533,"uid":275197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:29:21.000Z","msg":"你班廢老，人地好心良心價賣口罩，供貨有幾多就幾多都拎晒出黎。<br />\n買唔到就發撚晒老皮，想拎啲良心出黎都要畀人屌。<br />\n一係話人無講供貨量，有講貨量又屌人地少。<br />\n賣畀醫護優先又屌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正苦呢？無攞過出黎畀你用喎。<br />\n正當啲舖頭張羅緊搵到口罩，你老母，而家先話睇到口罩有需要。<br />\n啱呀，支持你地既正苦啦。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，買撚到你地咁忟，不撚如價高者得啦，大家都唔撚洗煩。夠撚晒公平未？<br />\n反而賣到貴一貴果啲藥房，又唔見你屌喎。<br />\n<br />\n無口罩畀你既政府你唔屌；<br />\n賣貴口罩畀你既藥房你唔屌；<br />\n賣黑心口罩果啲你又唔屌；<br />\n專捉撚住有良心既人黎屌！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實個道理同醫護罷工一撚樣。做嘢既實幹既就畀人任屌。<br />\n屌啦，屌啦，最好屌撚到更多醫護罷工，到時多撚謝你地呢班藍絲核彈。<br />\n支持醫護罷工<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f70a83ded00888c21adf325fc55a3e165c0ca09","tid":1851533,"uid":283700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:37:31.000Z","msg":"拍賣fitfit"},{"pid":"bbf1ae58edfb00625fdf763e6a5e13d941e46d33","tid":1851533,"uid":233367,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:37:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tOlEH28zQ0o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtOlEH28zQ0o&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rByAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=7a722e6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tOlEH28zQ0o</a><br />\n<br />\n好似呢位巴打咁大大聲屌9啲藍屍廢老就啱啦！"},{"pid":"7641d62e7d03ddf44e8812e3eb945dc70cb2cd00","tid":1851533,"uid":21052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:45:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes10.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes20.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes50.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes100.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes500.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cc12da90880278247d0ee04c1d7e403aef2f06e","tid":1851533,"uid":2142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:47:04.000Z","msg":"大家一齊嗌！「高官廢人！還罩於民！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1851544\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1851544</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}